00:22:54,190 --> 00:22:56,460
If you leave,

581
00:22:57,000 --> 00:22:59,100
there will be no plaintiff in this case,

582
00:22:59,310 --> 00:23:01,000
and it will get dismissed.

583
00:23:01,680 --> 00:23:03,000
All our

584
00:23:03,110 --> 00:23:04,400
hard work will be in vain,

585
00:23:04,400 --> 00:23:05,960
and we won't get a single cent back.

586
00:23:06,210 --> 00:23:07,240
People will say that

587
00:23:07,240 --> 00:23:09,000
our abilities as lawyers are lacking.

588
00:23:09,270 --> 00:23:10,580
You, as the plaintiff,

589
00:23:10,610 --> 00:23:12,110
aren't paying attention to this,

590
00:23:12,270 --> 00:23:14,640
