00:24:13,790 --> 00:24:15,510
and they are still living well.

605
00:24:17,410 --> 00:24:19,450
So you should live your life to the fullest.

606
00:24:24,780 --> 00:24:25,490
Even if

607
00:24:26,200 --> 00:24:29,030
we're left with just a breath after being hurt by bad people,

608
00:24:29,160 --> 00:24:30,400
