660
00:26:52,440 --> 00:26:54,680
Let's save some money first.

661
00:26:58,960 --> 00:27:00,920
How much can a child spend?

662
00:27:01,040 --> 00:27:02,670
I'm saving it now.

663
00:27:14,640 --> 00:27:16,310
Keep the summons.

664
00:27:18,200 --> 00:27:18,990
Director Han.

665
00:27:19,750 --> 00:27:20,590
See you in court.

666
00:27:23,200 --> 00:27:23,990
Mr. Han,

667
00:27:24,200 --> 00:27:25,110
