668
00:27:25,110 --> 00:27:25,880
Yingzi,

669
00:27:26,110 --> 00:27:28,160
who do you think

670
00:27:28,160 --> 00:27:29,680
has been helping us behind the scenes?

671
00:27:30,350 --> 00:27:31,350
Also, Mr. Tian,

672
00:27:31,510 --> 00:27:32,550
