682
00:27:59,480 --> 00:28:01,440
The remaining two properties will be given to the male party.

683
00:28:03,590 --> 00:28:04,400
Well.

684
00:28:04,600 --> 00:28:05,600
I understand.

685
00:28:05,620 --> 00:28:07,970
Given the company's financial status,

686
00:28:08,430 --> 00:28:10,080
