689
00:28:14,710 --> 00:28:15,280
Fine.

690
00:28:15,310 --> 00:28:17,160
Also, aside from the payment

691
00:28:17,180 --> 00:28:18,650
made to your uncle's company,

692
00:28:18,680 --> 00:28:21,520
there's less than 2,000,000 left in the account.

693
00:28:21,540 --> 00:28:24,270
Do you think we should use this as working capital, or...

694
00:28:24,420 --> 00:28:25,620
Transfer it to Damin.

695
00:28:25,790 --> 00:28:26,920
If I keep it in my account,

696
00:28:26,920 --> 00:28:28,110
all the money in the company's account

697
00:28:28,110 --> 00:28:30,000
