701
00:28:36,070 --> 00:28:38,310
I'll revise it.

702
00:28:39,510 --> 00:28:40,920
But I want to remind both of you—

703
00:28:41,050 --> 00:28:43,040
I think you should keep some money

704
00:28:43,070 --> 00:28:45,070
in the company's account.

705
00:28:45,440 --> 00:28:46,790
After all, it is not good

706
00:28:46,790 --> 00:28:49,350
