707
00:28:49,350 --> 00:28:51,030
Yes, I understand.

708
00:28:51,030 --> 00:28:51,480
Okay.

709
00:28:51,480 --> 00:28:53,000
If there are no other issues,

710
00:28:53,030 --> 00:28:55,160
once I revise the agreement,

