00:29:35,440 --> 00:29:35,880
Okay.

731
00:29:38,270 --> 00:29:39,160
Let's go.

732
00:29:39,960 --> 00:29:40,750
Thank you.

733
00:29:41,030 --> 00:29:41,750
Take care.

734
00:29:41,750 --> 00:29:42,400
Okay, thank you.

735
00:29:42,400 --> 00:29:43,200
Take the documents.

736
00:29:47,060 --> 00:29:49,060
I really don't understand today's young people.

737
00:29:49,890 --> 00:29:50,740
Gosh.

738
00:29:52,790 --> 00:29:53,750
Let me see

739
00:29:53,890 --> 00:29:56,090
