00:30:10,580 --> 00:30:11,550
Let me take a call.

751
00:30:10,680 --> 00:30:11,920
[Mr. Xue]

752
00:30:14,720 --> 00:30:16,350
Hello, Mr. Han.

753
00:30:17,200 --> 00:30:19,060
