755
00:30:22,290 --> 00:30:22,850
No.

756
00:30:24,370 --> 00:30:25,160
I'm not going.

757
00:30:25,190 --> 00:30:26,390
Just tell them you can't find us.

758
00:30:26,660 --> 00:30:27,590
Let me tell you,

759
00:30:27,590 --> 00:30:29,590
