769
00:30:42,860 --> 00:30:43,970
Come to me now.

770
00:30:44,000 --> 00:30:45,930
Don't you want to know how we're going to handle the case next?

771
00:30:46,280 --> 00:30:48,460
Okay, I'll be right there.

