789
00:31:21,590 --> 00:31:23,000
No, Mr. Han.

790
00:31:23,070 --> 00:31:24,070
Didn't you teach us

791
00:31:24,070 --> 00:31:25,790
to hide as much as possible?

792
00:31:26,070 --> 00:31:26,920
Besides,

793
00:31:27,120 --> 00:31:28,070
