796
00:31:33,880 --> 00:31:35,030
When we first met,

797
00:31:35,030 --> 00:31:36,160
I made it very clear—

798
00:31:36,200 --> 00:31:37,410
this case is straightforward,

799
00:31:37,440 --> 00:31:39,310
