800
00:31:39,440 --> 00:31:40,350
If this goes to court,

801
00:31:40,370 --> 00:31:41,740
there's no way we'll win.

802
00:31:42,640 --> 00:31:43,440
That's right.

803
00:31:43,750 --> 00:31:45,750
