833
00:32:33,130 --> 00:32:34,210
I trusted you.

834
00:32:34,230 --> 00:32:36,120
I signed the agreement because I trusted you.

835
00:32:36,260 --> 00:32:37,260
But now,

836
00:32:37,400 --> 00:32:39,600
you're forcing me to raise the agency fee, right?

837
00:32:39,770 --> 00:32:40,700
If you think that way,

838
00:32:40,720 --> 00:32:42,320
I won't say anything.

839
00:32:42,350 --> 00:32:44,690
Let's just wait for the trial and lose the case.

840
00:32:51,830 --> 00:32:53,200
Mr. Han.

841
00:32:54,750 --> 00:32:56,510
I spent over 100,000 hiring you.

842
00:32:56,840 --> 00:32:58,760
